rs. We\nanalyze the conditions in which such a correction becomes negligible. We also\nstudy the coherences, in terms of the relative entropy of coherence developed\nby the evolved post-measurement state. We illustrate the results by analyzing a\ntwo-level system monitored by a simple meter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2022 17:20:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-27"}
