 functionalization of the particles with a\nfluorescent label revealed their potential in studying specific virus-related\ninteractions. Notably, the universal character of the developed synthesis\nmethod makes it potentially applicable for fabricating VLPs imitating other\nlife-threatening viruses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 14:50:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
